<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Never was there any intention of in any way influencing or thwarting your 
audit." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Mayor Tom Bradley, in a transcript of an interview with Los Angeles 
Controller Rick Tuttle concerning allegations by Tuttle that a mayor's aide 
tried to interfere with Tuttle's audit of a controversial African trade 
promotion task force. 
</P>
</TEXT>
