<HEADLINE>
<P>
PRESIDENT BUSH'S PLAN TO FIGHT DRUGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
President Bush gave us a very elegant speech on how he was going to fight the 
use of drugs. Let us not forget that as vice president he was in charge of the 
drug program and in eight years the use of drugs increased in the United 
States. 
</P>
<P>
LEO FRIEDMAN 
</P>
<P>
Mission Viejo 
</P>
