BASEBALL FANS MOURN LOSS OF COMMISSIONER WITH GENUINE SORROW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
When the shock wears off, Bart Giamatti's memory will turn into an everlasting 
legacy. 
</P>
