In his five months as commissioner, he proved to us that nobody could take away 
the pride and integrity of major league baseball. But most of all, he 
demonstrated to us how we should protect the game. His respect and love for the 
game showed us the perfect commissioner. We should take note, because we need 
more people in this world like Bart Giamatti. 
