17-3 loss at Newbury Park. ; Photo, Greg Ochoa of Agoura is unable to gain 
possession of a Josh Smaler pass in the first half of the Chargers' 17-3 loss 
to Newbury Park. BOB CAREY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
