<P>
Junior Vince Greco scored four goals to lead Crespi High to a 9-5 victory over 
host Montebello in a quarterfinal match of the Bell Gardens water polo 
tournament Friday. 
</P>
<P>
Crespi built a 5-2 lead in the second quarter and was never threatened. Junior 
Tom Kretzin added two goals and junior goalie Tim Behrens had nine saves for 
the Celts. 
