<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
OIL SPILLS -- ALASKA; EXXON VALDEZ (SHIP); IMMUNITY (LEGAL); ALASKA -- LAWS; 
HAZELWOOD, JOSEPH 
</P>
