Brouillet photograph at left. He captures a second surfer, right, who seems to 
momentarily defy gravity. ; Photo, Peter Brouillet picks spot near Huntington 
Beach Pier to set up Nikon F3 with 600-millimeter lens. GLENN KOENIG / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
